NOTE ON SCOPE
-------------
This Apache-2.0 license applies to the SOURCE CODE in this repository only.

The license of the base model weights (Boldt/Boldt-DC-350M) and of any trained
derivative weights is SEPARATE and MUST be verified before release. See
docs/adr/ADR-001-base-model-and-license.md. Do not assume the model weights are
Apache-2.0 until that ADR is resolved with a primary source.
